-- Author Huang On House of Bo, As Xilai Trial Nears (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-08-07T20:24:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-07/author-huang-on-house-of-bo-as-xilai-trial-nears-audio-.html
Wenguang Huang, co-author of "A Death
in the Lucky Holiday Hotel: Murder, Money, and an Epic Power 
Struggle in  China ," discusses his book and the significance of 
Chinese politician Bo Xilai's corruption trial. Huang talks with
Bloomberg's Kathleen Hays and Vonnie Quinn on Bloomberg Radio's 
"The Hays Advantage."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 16:24
 